01:45.880 --> 01:48.880
So very often when we're trading New York session

01:49.040 --> 01:53.040
We're looking to target maybe London highs or maybe London lows as our external liquidity

01:53.040 --> 01:57.040
Why? Because there is a lot of liquidity resting in both those highs and lows

