For that day

06:12.480 --> 06:14.480
And the previous day low is the lowest point

06:14.480 --> 06:16.480
In which price has traded to for that day

06:16.480 --> 06:18.480
It's going to be a very high probability draw on liquidity

06:18.480 --> 06:20.480
